Starring: Scott Tanner, Bo Matthews, Dean Flynn, Ty LeBeouf, Andrew Justice, Allen Silver, Brandon Monroe, Justin Riddick, Jesse Santana, Justin Burkeshire 

Joe Gage takes us to a weather-beaten barn, after the second devastating tornado in the area. With the owner of the property armed with a handy video camera, the plot takes off right away. In the ensuing action, the cam gets passed to whoever ...    Full Descriptionis the least busy with his hands at the time. You always hear about how disasters bring people together, but the very unorthodox ways these TitanMen comfort each other is probably not going to make it onto one of those feel-good newscasts. Even so, it looks like it feels really, really good. 

This is the only Justin Burkeshire video.
